. Use the retry button to check again.'=>'未检测到 SSL。使用重试按钮再次检查。','(Unknown)'=>'（未知）','Install SSL certificate'=>'安装 SSL 证书','Retry'=>'重试','An SSL certificate has been detected'=>'已检测到 SSL 证书','Or set your wp-config.php to writable and reload this page.'=>'或者将您的 wp-config.php 文件设置为可写，并重载当前页面。','Add the following lines of code to your wp-config.php.'=>'将下列几行代码添加到您的 wp-config.php文件。','To set the httponly secure cookie settings, your wp-config.php has to be edited, but the file is not writable.'=>'要调整httponly安全cookie设置，您的wp-config.php文件需要被编辑，但是该文件不可写。','HttpOnly Secure cookies not set.'=>'HttpOnly 安全cookies未设置。','Due to a recent update by WP Engine, we have changed your settings automatically to adapt.'=>'由于最近的WP Engine更新，我们已经修改了您的设置以自动适应这个更新。','The Really Simple SSL plugin folder in the /wp-content/plugins/ directory has been renamed to %s. This might cause issues when deactivating, or with premium add-ons. To fix this you can rename the Really Simple SSL folder back to the default %s.'=>'/wp-content/plugins/ 目录下的Really Simple SSL 插件文件夹已经改名为 %s。这可能在重新激活或豪华版附加组件时会导致问题。要修复这个，您可以重命名 Really Simple SSL 文件夹为默认的 %s。','Not all recommended security headers are installed'=>'未安装所有推荐的安全头部','SSL Status Test'=>'SSL状态测试','Recommended security headers installed'=>'检测到建议的安全标头','The recommended security headers are detected on your site.'=>'在您的站点上检测到建议的安全标头。','Security Headers Test'=>'测试安全标头','No SSL detected'=>'未检测到SSL','Learn more about security headers'=>'了解有关安全标头的详细信息','Enable 301 redirect'=>'启用301重定向','To ensure all traffic passes through SSL, please enable a 301 redirect.'=>'为确保所有流量通过SSL，请启用301重定向。','No 301 redirect to SSL enabled.'=>'没有301重定向到SSL启用。','Really Simple SSL is installed, but no valid SSL certificate is detected.'=>'安装了非常简单的SSL，但是没有检测到有效的SSL证书。','Really Simple SSL detected an SSL certificate, but has not been configured to enforce SSL.'=>'Really Simple SSL检测到SSL证书，但尚未配置为强制SSL。','SSL is not enabled.'=>'SSL未启用。','Completed'=>'完成','Install'=>'安装','Installed'=>'已安装','Open'=>'打开','Warning'=>'警告','WordPress 301 redirect enabled. We recommend to enable a 301 .htaccess redirect.'=>'WordPress 301 重定向已启用。我们建议启用 301 .htaccess 重定向。','Your site uses Divi. This can require some additional steps before getting the secure lock.'=>'您的网站使用了Divi。这可能需要额外的设置，才能获得安全防护。','Your site uses Elementor. This can require some additional steps before getting the secure lock.'=>'您的网站正在使用Elementor。这可能需要额外的设置，才能获得安全防护。','SSL is enabled networkwide.'=>'网络范围内启用了SSL。','Activate SSL'=>'激活SSL','Basic SSL configuration finished! Improve your score with %sReally Simple SSL Pro%s.'=>'SSL基础设置完成！使用 %sReally Simple SSL Pro%s 获取更佳表现。','General'=>'一般','Mixed content fixer not enabled. Enable the option to fix mixed content on your site.'=>'混合内容修复未启用。启用该选项以修复您网站上的混合内容。','No recommended redirect rules detected.'=>'未检测到推荐的重定向规则。','Read more'=>'阅读更多','Really Simple SSL has received no response from the webpage.'=>'Really Simple SSL 未接收到网页响应。','SSL configuration finished!'=>'SSL设置完成！','SSL is activated on your site.'=>'SSL在您的网站激活。','SSL is not enabled yet.'=>'SSL尚未启用。','SSL is not yet enabled on this site.'=>'SSL尚未在该网站启用。','Support'=>'支持','The mixed content fixer is active, but was not detected on the frontpage.'=>'混合内容修复已启用，但是无法在前端页面检测到。','You still have %s task open.'=>'您尚有 %s 个打开任务。','Really Simple Plugins'=>'Really Simple Plugins','Hi, Really Simple SSL has kept your site secure for some time now, awesome! If you have a moment, please consider leaving a review on WordPress.org to spread the word. We greatly appreciate it! If you have any questions or feedback, leave us a %smessage%s.'=>'嗨，Really Simple SSL已经使您的网站安全了一段时间了，太棒了！ 如果有时间，请考虑在WordPress.org上发表评论以广而告之。 非常感谢！ 如果您有任何疑问或反馈，请和我们%s联络%s。','Check out Really Simple SSL Pro'=>'查看Really Simple SSL Pro','Don\'t show again'=>'不再显示','The mixed content fixer could not be detected due to a cURL error: %s. cURL errors are often caused by an outdated version of PHP or cURL and don\'t affect the front-end of your site. Contact your hosting provider for a fix.'=>'由于一个 cURL 错误：%s，混合内容修复无法检测。cURL 错误常常是由于旧版的 PHP 或 cURL导致，不会影响到您网站的前端。请联系您的空间服务商寻求修复。','Error occurred when retrieving the webpage.'=>'获取网页时发生错误。','You have set a 301 redirect to SSL. This is important for SEO purposes'=>'您已为SSL设置了一个301重定向。这对于SEO而言很重要','Enable'=>'启用','301 SSL redirect enabled'=>'已启用301 SSL重定向','301 .htaccess redirect is not enabled.'=>'301 .htaccess重定向未启用。','The 301 .htaccess redirect is the fastest and most reliable redirect option.'=>'301 .htaccess 重定向通常是最快且最可靠的重定向方法。','The \'force-deactivate.php\' file has to be renamed to .txt. Otherwise your ssl can be deactivated by anyone on the internet.'=>'\'force-deactivate.php\'文件必须重命名为.txt。 否则，互联网上的任何人都可以停用您的ssl。','Maybe later'=>'也许以后','Leave a review'=>'发表评论','Hi, Really Simple SSL has kept your site secure for a month now, awesome! If you have a moment, please consider leaving a review on WordPress.org to spread the word. We greatly appreciate it! If you have any questions or feedback, leave us a %smessage%s.'=>'嗨，你现在已经使用Really Simple SSL一个月了，棒极了！如果您有时间，请考虑在WordPress.org上留下评论来宣传。我们非常感谢！如果您有任何问题或反馈，请给我们留言%s信息%s。','Activate SSL per site or install a wildcard certificate to fix this.'=>'逐一每站开启 SSL或安装一反遮罩凭证来修护。','This leads to issues when activating SSL networkwide since subdomains will be forced over SSL as well while they don\'t have a valid certificate.'=>'这会在启动 SSL 网际网路时导致些问题，因为子网域也会被强制通过 SSL，而且它并没有有效的 SSL 凭证。','You run a Multisite installation with subdomains, but your site doesn\'t have a wildcard certificate.'=>'透过子网域你执行多重式网站的安装，但是你的网站没有反遮罩凭证。','Cancel'=>'取消','More info'=>'更多资料','Really Simple SSL and Really Simple SSL add-ons do not process any personal identifiable information, so the GDPR does not apply to these plugins or usage of these plugins on your website. You can find our privacy policy <a href="%s" target="_blank">here</a>.'=>'Really Simple SSL 和Really Simple SSL 附加组件不会处理任何个人身份信息，因此GDPR不适用于这些插件或在您的网站上使用这些插件。您可以在这里找到我们的<a href="%s" target="_blank">隐私政策</a>。','https://really-simple-plugins.com'=>'https://really-simple-plugins.com','Learn more'=>'读取更多','You can also let the automatic scan of the pro version handle this for you, and get premium support, increased security with HSTS and more!'=>'你只能让进阶版本的自动扫瞄帮儗处理这个，以及取得优质支持，用HSTS提高的保全系统以及更多!','You may need to login in again.'=>'你可能必须再登入一次。','Enable 301 .htaccess redirect'=>'启动301.htaccess导向','No 301 redirect is set. Enable the WordPress 301 redirect in the settings to get a 301 permanent redirect.'=>'301导向没有被设定。请在设定中取得一301永久导向以启动WordPress 301导向。','301 redirect to https set.'=>'301重定向到https设置。','View settings page'=>'查看设置页面','Premium Support'=>'优质支援服務','SSL is enabled on your site.'=>'SSL 已能在你网站使用','Instructions'=>'指示程序','Your wp-config.php has to be edited, but is not writable.'=>'你的wp-config.php 必须要编辑，可是并非可写。','Almost ready to migrate to SSL!'=>'几乎准备好要迁移到 SSL!','%s is a singleton class and you cannot create a second instance.'=>'%s是一个单例级而你无法新增第二个执行个体。','Images, stylesheets or scripts from a domain without an SSL certificate: remove them or move to your own server.'=>'没有 SSL 凭证的网域图片，样式表或脚本: 删除或搬移它们到你的伺服器。','Http references in your .css and .js files: change any http:// into https://'=>'关于 .css 及 .js 文件的 http 参考：将所有的 http:// 替换为 //','Mixed content fixer was successfully detected on the front-end.'=>'已成功在前端检测到 mixed content 修复器。','Really Simple SSL'=>'Really Simple SSL','https://really-simple-ssl.com'=>'https://really-simple-ssl.com','Stop editing the .htaccess file'=>'停止编辑 .htaccess 档案','An SSL certificate was detected on your site.'=>'在您的网站上检测到SSL证书。','No SSL detected.'=>'未检测到SSL。','Settings'=>'設定','Mixed content fixer'=>'混合内容修复程序','Activate networkwide to fix this.'=>'启动广域网路来修复这个。','Because the $_SERVER["HTTPS"] variable is not set, your website may experience redirect loops.'=>'因为这$_SERVER["HTTPS"] 变数尚未设好，你的网站可能会经历重导向回圈。','Check again'=>'再检查一遍','You run a Multisite installation with subfolders, which prevents this plugin from fixing your missing server variable in the wp-config.php.'=>'你用子资料夹去执行多站点的安装，会阻止这插件修复你在 wp-config.php 里遗失的伺服器变数。']];